{"tid":343993,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學車真係唔好去鴨架","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:39:35.000Z","uid":129699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fbe576e7bd26fcb08c2f525fd183d36eae34a4","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"本身舊場已經細，依家搬咗仲細<br />\n46 泊車排餐死<br />\n26打8字個個位又難入<br />\n考試仲要同練車個啲掙黎用<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住路試易<br />\n又多死車又多車，路又窄<br />\n<br />\n考官仲要嚴過其他考場好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n46都仲可以去試下<br />\n26真係出去學算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f0aaf98c7bd252b13e6ceb0d093f941498d9a1","tid":343993,"uid":7155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身舊場已經細，依家搬咗仲細<br />\n46 泊車排餐死<br />\n26打8字個個位又難入<br />\n考試仲要同練車個啲掙黎用<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住路試易<br />\n又多死車又多車，路又窄<br />\n<br />\n考官仲要嚴過其他考場好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n46都仲可以去試下<br />\n26真係出去學算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鴨駕真係難考咗好多<br />\n我有幾個fd 近期考都肥<br />\n好似啲官執得仲嚴過出面"},{"pid":"12de772945bc6ff2b9d7830271a11a6176eb37ce","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身舊場已經細，依家搬咗仲細<br />\n46 泊車排餐死<br />\n26打8字個個位又難入<br />\n考試仲要同練車個啲掙黎用<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住路試易<br />\n又多死車又多車，路又窄<br />\n<br />\n考官仲要嚴過其他考場好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n46都仲可以去試下<br />\n26真係出去學算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鴨駕真係難考咗好多<br />\n我有幾個fd 近期考都肥<br />\n好似啲官執得仲嚴過出面</blockquote><br />\n依家個場根本就唔夠位，電單車個邊直頭夾硬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔夠呀sir 教，約咗上堂都可以朝早打黎話呀sir 請病假要改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網約得既堂少得可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港島區真係出去考冇咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ee2e83644cf21f21a6335be64f27d491022edb","tid":343993,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"仲諗住易考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我12月考好驚"},{"pid":"5690ee1c78278014ec567572492a7542d027b674","tid":343993,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:41:05.000Z","msg":"十年前你係個度1 tick pass"},{"pid":"53b98b1bb3d1f4fcdff5749e431c9a6f17c08f08","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十年前你係個度1 tick pass</blockquote><br />\n依家啲官好似唔想比個牌你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝去學車，26成朝得一個合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係羊<br />\n<br />\n出去練車，見啲貨車佬來回兩條線都兩邊hea 晒啲貨出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人打去報警先好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11057eda276938678915a62ad74a5d75494325e9","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住易考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我12月考好驚</blockquote><br />\n考46 定26？<br />\n46都仲可以，因為都只係塞車同過死車<br />\n26就勸你轉去沙田算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea03484a0357d10f471295d39b6ab83bae3c7a32","tid":343993,"uid":41695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年前你係個度1 tick pass</blockquote><br />\n依家啲官好似唔想比個牌你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝去