ckquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀巴打<br />\n相逢何必曾相識？</blockquote><br />\n幾時考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f399c20e4ded9d95f9368046439cf368b55938","tid":343993,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"我係學學下26轉左新場，8字係難左，但其他冇分別， 反而要留意一出去果d泊緊車既學神46。 唔係未出街已經即刻fail"},{"pid":"ed30031f80d76e13ae687be793c456dcb5dd70c7","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十年前你係個度1 tick pass</blockquote><br />\n依家啲官好似唔想比個牌你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝去學車，26成朝得一個合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係羊<br />\n<br />\n出去練車，見啲貨車佬來回兩條線都兩邊hea 晒啲貨出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人打去報警先好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去學26？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀巴打<br />\n相逢何必曾相識？</blockquote><br />\n幾時考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n九月"},{"pid":"532db4e6ef26c82cc4ea1d004be8eff2c8f23253","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係學學下26轉左新場，8字係難左，但其他冇分別， 反而要留意一出去果d泊緊車既學神46。 唔係未出街已經即刻fail</blockquote><br />\n個位根本就西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沙田轉過去既話就知個分別有幾大<br />\n沙田淨係八字斜坡都有兩個，一邊比練車另一邊考車，依家你就考都仲要等練車既打完先熱到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鴨架電單車唔好話要兩個斜坡，淨係打完八字轉出去路試個條路都已經夠西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出路試比沙田轉線少，冇燈位<br />\n但兩條考線其實係同一條唔同路口次序<br />\n啲學車塞住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去親鴨架學個啲都係啲姐姐仔多，又騰雞又亂黎<br />\n個個讓路位，路口都係塞塞塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n路窄仲要多貨車死車，如果你覺得沙田銀城線已經係難既話，你諗下自己前後都係依啲貨車學車你就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要因爲場地細，你46想練泊車都係要排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗你一堂塞車排隊都用咗半堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電單車八字就度度都要排隊，但連考之前都要排就轆柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講話難過出面<br />\n但唔係大家想像中咁好<br />\n如果諗住黎依度一take pass，我諗你一係去沙田一係出去勤力啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a30f97ec3da431a2d2d2eeb4f88f711e52cb74","tid":343993,"uid":112814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"鴨駕46泊位掉頭應該係駕院入面最難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路試依然易到on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4e25b517fbf41a0a35cee74235de06c486011a","tid":343993,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2973cc09ea0e1677eb7708aa191e153df5142c0a","tid":343993,"uid":129699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>26打8字根本易到爆<br />\n新場1take pass<br />\n最緊要唔好驚</blockquote><br />\n有師兄係度考咗三次都唔pass<br />\n我問佢點解仲係道考，佢話因爲重考考期快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128d8bc56174531fde6baf4f98105683a2e76950","tid":343993,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"考官窮想賺人多幾堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d94c622c53c9adb772f4069ef7e99c87f2bf52e","tid":343993,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}